{"data":[{"id":564154264,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564154264","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546335929,"updated_time":1546335929,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"comment_count":2,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e小时候喜欢过数学。有意思，奇妙。高中的时候跟不上了，完全不想学，觉得除了难，没有意思了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以看不懂高中程度的数学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明本来就是让人证明的，谁都可以有理想有志愿，这是好事。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明的错误在于，数学可以说是种无限的学科，或者说，任何学科，只要钻研的足够深，会发现未知的东西更多。比起热情信心来，人更需要敬畏。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e三体也是个复杂的问题，虽然喜欢三体小说，但完全不懂三体问题的难度。小说里有句话叫，无知和弱小不是生存的障碍，傲慢才是。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e莫说证明不了，就是未来的某一天，某个人证明了，那也不是他她个人的成就，个人也是建立在前人知识积累上才能更进一步的，不是谁脱离社会凭空跳到一个高度。如果真的脱离于人类研究基础到达一个新高度，那就是异类文明了，近似于外星文明。地球上有没有不好说。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数学上下无限，数字可以是无限的，人类有限。除了已经有的猜想，还会有更难的猜想，过去多年后，现在的猜想都可能证明，那是知识积累的结果。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e懂的人懂就行了，不懂的人可以不懂，有懂的人就行了，不需要谁都懂。什么科学成就都是人类共同财富。我觉得做人要厚道，没必要对某个人错误的证明小题大做，好像要掀起全民批判似的，不利于学术自由。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果真的有本事，证明哥猜，不必揪住别人的错误当成话题。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"小时候喜欢过数学。有意思，奇妙。高中的时候跟不上了，完全不想学，觉得除了难，没有意思了。所以看不懂高中程度的数学。证明本来就是让人证明的，谁都可以有理想有志愿，这是好事。证明的错误在于，数学可以说是种无限的学科，或者说，任何学科，只要钻研…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=340\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark